text: Gei Rachel e dogi haga muliagina idimaa mee dela la gaa made, gei mee gaa gahi dana dama daane bolo Benoni,35.18 Benoni: Di ingoo deenei dono hadinga i nnelekai Hebrew boloo, “Tama o dogu Hagaduadua”. gei tamana o maa ga haga ingoo a mee bolo Benjamin.35.18 Benjamin: Di ingoo deenei dono hadinga i nnelekai Hebrew boloo, “Tama dela ga Haadanga lamalia”.
